            "href": "#",
            "title": "Server-First Pattern",
            "description": "The application follows a server-first pattern where rendering, data fetching, and security checks happen on the server by default. Client-side interactivity is added only where needed.\n\nThis approach improves performance, security, and SEO while reducing JavaScript bundle size.",
