            "title": "Defense-in-Depth Security",
            "description": "Security is implemented at multiple layers: server-side validation, Zod schema validation, React Server Actions, CSRF protection, and runtime type guards.\n\nNo single point of failure - compromising one layer doesn't expose the system.",
